Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Knowledge Ontology Module Stub
Provides comprehensive ontology construction, reasoning, and validation capabilities
Enables OWL, RDF, SPARQL support, and distributed ontology management
:End Note

Type OntologySystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    ontology_language as String
    ontology_store as OntologyStore
    reasoning_engine as ReasoningEngine
    query_processor as QueryProcessor
    validation_framework as ValidationFramework
    alignment_system as AlignmentSystem
    evolution_manager as EvolutionManager
    mapping_engine as MappingEngine
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type OntologyStore is Dictionary with:
    store_id as String
    storage_type as String
    storage_backend as String
    namespace_management as NamespaceManagement
    versioning_system as VersioningSystem
    indexing_strategy as IndexingStrategy
    compression_settings as CompressionSettings
    backup_configuration as BackupConfiguration

Type Ontology is Dictionary with:
    ontology_id as String
    ontology_iri as String
    ontology_name as String
    ontology_version as String
    ontology_language as String
    classes as List[OntologyClass]
    properties as List[OntologyProperty]
    individuals as List[Individual]
    axioms as List[Axiom]
    annotations as List[Annotation]
    imports as List[ImportDeclaration]
    prefixes as Dictionary

Type OntologyClass is Dictionary with:
    class_id as String
    class_iri as String
    class_name as String
    class_type as String
    super_classes as List[OntologyClass]
    sub_classes as List[OntologyClass]
    equivalent_classes as List[OntologyClass]
    disjoint_classes as List[OntologyClass]
    class_expressions as List[ClassExpression]
    class_axioms as List[ClassAxiom]
    annotations as List[Annotation]

Type OntologyProperty is Dictionary with:
    property_id as String
    property_iri as String
    property_name as String
    property_type as String
    domain as List[OntologyClass]
    range as List[OntologyClass]
    super_properties as List[OntologyProperty]
    sub_properties as List[OntologyProperty]
    equivalent_properties as List[OntologyProperty]
    property_characteristics as PropertyCharacteristics
    property_axioms as List[PropertyAxiom]

Type Individual is Dictionary with:
    individual_id as String
    individual_iri as String
    individual_name as String
    individual_type as String
    class_assertions as List[ClassAssertion]
    property_assertions as List[PropertyAssertion]
    same_individuals as List[Individual]
    different_individuals as List[Individual]
    annotations as List[Annotation]

Type Axiom is Dictionary with:
    axiom_id as String
    axiom_type as String
    axiom_content as AxiomContent
    axiom_annotations as List[Annotation]
    axiom_source as AxiomSource
    axiom_confidence as Float
    logical_strength as String

Type ReasoningEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine_id as String
    reasoning_type as String
    reasoner_implementation as String
    supported_profiles as List[String]
    inference_capabilities as List[InferenceCapability]
    consistency_checking as ConsistencyChecking
    entailment_checking as EntailmentChecking
    classification_engine as ClassificationEngine
    realization_engine as RealizationEngine

Type QueryProcessor is Dictionary with:
    processor_id as String
    query_languages as List[QueryLanguage]
    query_optimizers as List[QueryOptimizer]
    result_formatters as List[ResultFormatter]
    caching_system as CachingSystem
    query_analytics as QueryAnalytics

Type ValidationFramework is Dictionary with:
    framework_id as String
    validation_rules as List[ValidationRule]
    validation_engine as ValidationEngine
    quality_metrics as List[QualityMetric]
    validation_reports as List[ValidationReport]
    compliance_checking as ComplianceChecking

Type AlignmentSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    alignment_algorithms as List[AlignmentAlgorithm]
    alignment_metrics as List[AlignmentMetric]
    alignment_validation as AlignmentValidation
    alignment_optimization as AlignmentOptimization
    cross_reference_management as CrossReferenceManagement

Type EvolutionManager is Dictionary with:
    manager_id as String
    evolution_history as List[EvolutionEvent]
    change_management as ChangeManagement
    version_control as VersionControl
    impact_analysis as ImpactAnalysis
    rollback_capabilities as RollbackCapabilities

Type MappingEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine_id as String
    mapping_algorithms as List[MappingAlgorithm]
    mapping_rules as List[MappingRule]
    mapping_validation as MappingValidation
    mapping_optimization as MappingOptimization
    cross_reference_management as CrossReferenceManagement

Type SystemConfiguration is Dictionary with:
    config_id as String
    system_parameters as Dictionary
    performance_settings as PerformanceSettings
    security_settings as SecuritySettings
    integration_settings as IntegrationSettings
    monitoring_settings as MonitoringSettings

Process called "create_ontology_system" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "construct_ontology" that takes ontology_system as Dictionary and construction_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "define_classes_and_hierarchy" that takes ontology_system as Dictionary and structure_design as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "define_properties_and_hierarchy" that takes ontology_system as Dictionary and class_definition as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_ontology_reasoning" that takes ontology_system as Dictionary and reasoning_query as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "align_ontologies" that takes ontology_system as Dictionary and alignment_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "validate_ontology" that takes ontology_system as Dictionary and validation_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "evolve_ontology" that takes ontology_system as Dictionary and evolution_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "query_ontology" that takes ontology_system as Dictionary and query_specification as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_ontology_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_ontology_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 